{"tid":1005050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強到內蒙古考察春運唔搭高鐵，問民工搵工易唔易攞唔攞到人工","createTime":"2019-02-02T03:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T07:28:51.000Z","uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5e47ed3d7d1b70ab545c9fe4566ac68fe00da33f","tid":1005050,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:00:34.000Z","msg":"據中國政府網，2月1日下午5時，包頭開往大連的K1567次列車停靠在內蒙古集寧南站，中共國務院總理李克強登上4號車廂，看望慰問旅客和乘務人員，考察春運保障情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2019-02/02/5363247/images/126de29dbf82405f9933c0a54a3f37f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fxinwen%2F2019-02%2F02%2F5363247%2Fimages%2F126de29dbf82405f9933c0a54a3f37f2.jpg&h=eb4fa0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李克強問在座的有沒有農民工，幾位旅客舉起了手。他關切詢問他們工資是否足額拿到，在外打工有什麼難處，工作好不好找。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2019-02/02/5363247/images/d33721fddc0640a98462be0ef75a027b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fxinwen%2F2019-02%2F02%2F5363247%2Fimages%2Fd33721fddc0640a98462be0ef75a027b.jpg&h=edd306cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得知這趟列車要經停26站、歷時30多個小時，李克強說，我們現在雖然有了時速350公里的高速列車，但不能沒有逢站就停、票價低廉的綠皮車。<br />\n<br />\n他還說，因為我們國家很大，還是一個發展中國家，發展還很不平衡很不充分，既要考慮效率，又要兼顧公平。列車雖有不同，但最終目的都是要把站台上不同需求的旅客安全送達。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://big5.www.gov.cn/gate/big5/www.gov.cn/premier/2019-02/02/5363241/images/a5f6cf49e525459ea39b2c0aff107b9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.www.gov.cn%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fpremier%2F2019-02%2F02%2F5363241%2Fimages%2Fa5f6cf49e525459ea39b2c0aff107b9a.jpg&h=2613feaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綠皮車在20世紀90年代以前，曾是中國鐵路最具代表性的列車。綠皮車通常無空調，車窗可打開，幾乎各站都停，是中國基層人民返鄉的重要交通工具。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2019-02/02/content_5363247.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fxinwen%2F2019-02%2F02%2Fcontent_5363247.htm&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=388b6363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2019-02/02/content_5363247.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bf027b8f8d04477659ee73b9064690ba4223ac89","tid":1005050,"uid":65984,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"一班唔會開出既列車加一群演員, 做完戲影完相再去搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524c0fd859da55cd822d41002ab2d4b27676ee65","tid":1005050,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf027b8f8d04477659ee73b9064690ba4223ac89","tid":1005050,"uid":65984,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"一班唔會開出既列車加一群演員, 做完戲影完相再去搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7406c8b34a4055d04a1af4e63b5d9d04e1210c","tid":1005050,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf027b8f8d04477659ee73b9064690ba4223ac89","tid":1005050,"uid":65984,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"一班唔會開出既列車加一群演員, 做完戲影完相再去搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7938b30af76bc73fb750cdeb5a46d535e4ff7b31","tid":1005050,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5500be3d9810b60f5de05994ddd01da9f312caa2","tid":1005050,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"軟座黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682432550a0998d7d9a12aaf13c9375e7fa57dc7","tid":1005050,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"集集連依啲戲都冇做下。"},{"pid":"99e54b4b6c35d84f94267bf325190f469e98c853","tid":1005050,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"架車擺明係新車卡黎<br />\n加埋鐵路部各家屬演員....咁就叫新聞"},{"pid":"5fdab06964a0fb7a3383979ce74c5a321d3d6670","tid":1005050,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"682432550a0998d7d9a12aaf13c9375e7fa57dc7","tid":1005050,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"集集連依啲戲都冇做下。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"每年新春到來之際，中共領導人都會有走訪基層的活動，今年也不例外。<br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平今天上午就到北京前門，與群眾包餃子，祝賀新年，上演十足的親民秀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/01/realtime/5876823.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F01%2Frealtime%2F5876823.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=00ae41db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為中國央視習近平北京前門與民眾包餃子圖片<br />\n<br />\n據央視新聞，今天上午，習近平來到北京前門東區，沿草廠四條胡同步行察看街巷風貌，走進居民家中看望慰問，了解居民生活情況。<br />\n<br />\n習近平還與群眾一起包餃子、拉家常(聊家常事)，並向大家致以新春祝福。<br />\n<br />\n消息沒有提及習近平是否與民眾一起吃餃子，以及北京當地是否布防了嚴密的安全措施。<br />\n<br />\nsource(法國國際廣播電台): <a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20190201-習近平今往北京前門民家包餃子親民秀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20190201-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%BE%80%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%89%8D%E9%96%80%E6%B0%91%E5%AE%B6%E5%8C%85%E9%A4%83%E5%AD%90%E8%A6%AA%E6%B0%91%E7%A7%80&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=e82b282a\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20190201-習近平今往北京前門民家包餃子親民秀</a>"},{"pid":"247444f9fb68da9786ebfe0cd1df46464136e191","tid":1005050,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"有冇用過火車個廁所先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7092e6fdb513e62624ab88d9730520754fb086","tid":1005050,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"真係似搵佢頂刁帝個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0972ae320d87d5a6a37347d0f00449fd02bdee23","tid":1005050,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"架車新到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班都係戲子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}